{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"794c1aee65","title":"右派言论——“共产党用不着你时就一脚踢开”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"254f30c62d","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"794c1aee65"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"f4ddff680b","name":"朱先煌"},{"id":"ffe82e1d66","name":"山西农学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6927beec1f","type":"title","text":"右派言论——“共产党用不着你时就一脚踢开”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"794c1aee65"},{"id":"d48928475a","type":"authors","text":"山西农学院朱先煌","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"794c1aee65"},{"id":"5d7745ef28","type":"subtitle","text":"（朱先煌：山西农学院教务长、民盟支部主任委员）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"794c1aee65"},{"id":"77d7e741e7","type":"paragraph","text":"共产党就是这样，用着知识分子了，就抱在怀里给你住最好的房子，用不着你时，就一脚踢开；党虽然给了知识分子很高的地位，但是有职无权，没有重视，没有温暖，相反还给挂上了个“可疑人”的牌子，一直没有给摘下来。因此，知识分子对党的态度是“有情芍药含春泪，无力蔷薇卧晚枝”。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"794c1aee65"},{"id":"77394329aa","type":"paragraph","text":"靠近党的知识分子有“泪”，积极性提不起来，和党有距离的知识分子更是卧倒了，没有一点积极性。知识分子的自尊心被损害了。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"794c1aee65"},{"id":"093ed6103f","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《“鸣”、“放”选集（二）》（中共山西省委整风办公室编，1957年9月）。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"794c1aee65"}],"page":{"id":"2f932e06bd","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"794c1aee65","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}